Subject: [PATCH 0841/1168] mmc: core: fix race condition in mmc_wait_data_done

commit 71f8a4b81d040b3d094424197ca2f1bf811b1245 upstream.

The following panic is captured in ker3.14, but the issue still exists
in latest kernel.
